the new land ( swedish : &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ) is a 1972 swedish film co-written and directed by jan troell and starring max von sydow , liv ullmann and eddie &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . the film is a sequel to troell 's 1971 film the emigrants , and both are based on the emigrants novels by &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . drawing its story from the last two novels , the settlers and the last letter home , the film is about the swedish immigrants establishing their home in minnesota , during the dakota war of 1862 . the film was nominated for the academy award for best foreign language film . it and the emigrants are the basis for the 1974 american television series the new land .